\par \fs16 \pard \ql \li600\ri0 \sb120 \fi360 * Counsel of Record
\par \fs20 \pard \ql \li0\ri0 \sb120 \fi360 NOLAN A. BOWIE, J.D., Temple University, 220 Tomlinson Theatre, Philadelphia, PA 19122
